of the Lingyue Clan.

546
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:07,120
It can test a lover's sincerity.

547
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:10,050
Each person in a couple has one.

548
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:12,320
It's because if either of them lies,

549
00:38:13,110 --> 00:38:15,480
